            "stanza_text": "En cette minute dernière\nDe l'an maudit mil neuf cent deux,\nRemontons d'un siècle en arrière\nPour voir un contraste hideux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Ainsi qu'un astre, la cocarde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Au chapeau du Consul flambait.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "— Quelle honte, quand on regarde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "L'accordéon du vieux Loubet !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ainsi qu'un astre, la cocarde\nAu chapeau du Consul flambait.\n— Quelle honte, quand on regarde\nL'accordéon du vieux Loubet !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Absous, sans renier ses maîtres,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "L'émigré revenait au nid.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "— On ne fait plus grâce qu'aux traîtres.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Déroulède est toujours proscrit.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Absous, sans renier ses maîtres,\nL'émigré revenait au nid.\n— On ne fait plus grâce qu'aux traîtres.\nDéroulède est toujours proscrit."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Le traité d'Amiens, quel beau songe !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "La paix dans la gloire, à jamais !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "— Jaurès veut qu'on passe l'éponge",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Sur votre espoir, Strasbourg et Metz !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le traité d'Amiens, quel beau songe !\nLa paix dans la gloire, à jamais !\n— Jaurès veut qu'on passe l'éponge\nSur votre espoir, Strasbourg et Metz !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "La foule priait, accourue",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Autour de l'Autel relevé.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "— On jette les sœurs dans la rue",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Et les pauvres sur le pavé.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La foule priait, accourue\nAutour de l'Autel relevé.\n— On jette les sœurs dans la rue\nEt les pauvres sur le pavé."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Sur le drapeau qu'un souffle gonfle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Le peuple lisait : « Marengo ».",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "— Aujourd'hui, quand le tambour ronfle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "« Fachoda ! » murmure l'écho.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sur le drapeau qu'un souffle gonfle,\nLe peuple lisait : « Marengo ».\n— Aujourd'hui, quand le tambour ronfle,\n« Fachoda ! » murmure l'écho."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Qu'il sonnait bien, le sabre courbe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Des chefs d'Arcole et d'Aboukir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "— L'or qu'empile un Juif sale et fourbe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "A présent, fait seul tressaillir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Qu'il sonnait bien, le sabre courbe\nDes chefs d'Arcole et d'Aboukir !\n— L'or qu'empile un Juif sale et fourbe,\nA présent, fait seul tressaillir."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Les pillages du Directoire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Cessaient, sur des ordres formels.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "— On sera doux, veuillez le croire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Pour les escrocs officiels.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les pillages du Directoire\nCessaient, sur des ordres formels.\n— On sera doux, veuillez le croire,\nPour les escrocs officiels."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Quoi ? C'est vrai, tant d'ignominie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "C'est dans ce bourbier que roula",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "La pauvre France à l'agonie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Après cent ans, elle en est là !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quoi ? C'est vrai, tant d'ignominie !\nC'est dans ce bourbier que roula\nLa pauvre France à l'agonie !\nAprès cent ans, elle en est là !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Mais une espérance obstinée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Tourne nos yeux vers l'avenir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "N'est-ce pas, ô nouvelle année,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Que ce cauchemar va finir,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais une espérance obstinée\nTourne nos yeux vers l'avenir.\nN'est-ce pas, ô nouvelle année,\nQue ce cauchemar va finir,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Et que, bientôt, comme en brumaire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Quelques soldats, sortis des rangs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Vont — justice froide et sommaire —",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Crosser les reins de nos tyrans ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et que, bientôt, comme en brumaire,\nQuelques soldats, sortis des rangs,\nVont — justice froide et sommaire —\nCrosser les reins de nos tyrans ?"
        }
